# Personal routing hints

When a question names one of these projects or people, search the mapped
source(s) before saying you can't find it.

## Projects → sources
- **<Project A>** — Notion (documentation, meeting notes) · GitHub (code) · Drive (documents)
- **<Project B>** — Drive (documents)
- **<Project C>** — GitHub (code)

## Source specifics
- **Notion** — <which docs / workspaces live here>
- **Drive** — <which folders / topics>
- **GitHub** — <which repos / orgs>
- **Calendar** — events; the source for any "when" / "where" question.
- **Contacts** — birthdays, addresses, phone, and email.
